---
title: Feta-Turkey Meatballs  with Sundried Tomato Orzo
description: Dill-icious feta and spinach meatballs are the jewels in this Mediterranean dinner! Nestled on a bed of creamy sun-dried tomato pesto orzo, with a sprinkle of feta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1010_W29_CA_RT162075-1_Main_low-0aa226b5.jpg
